"""
Payment flow:
  1. Client calls POST /payments/initiate with booking_id + method
  2. For card/Stripe: we create a PaymentIntent and return client_secret to the frontend
  3. For FPX: we redirect to the FPX gateway URL
  4. For bank transfer: customer sends slip via WhatsApp/email and admin confirms
  5. Stripe / FPX callbacks hit POST /payments/webhook/{gateway}
  6. On success we mark payment as paid and booking as confirmed
"""

